MIP
multum in parvo
"much in little"

plugin wrappers, abstractions, simplifications, helpers, ..

v0.0.0
in progress, prototype, proof of concept, pre-, ..

# os

- linux
- (windows)

# plugin

- clap
- dssi
- exe
- ladspa
- lv2
- vst2
- vst3

# host

- clap
- dssi
- ladspa

# gui

- xcb
- cairo
- ctx
- (gdi)

# other

- header-only (except your plugin)
- low level, un-modern c++
- no weird/ugly build system
- few/no external dependencies
- 'fat' plugins (multiple plugin formats in one .so)
- multiple (indexed) sub-plugins
- no vst2 or vst3 sdk needed
- parameters w/auto-conversion
- midi input, mpe
- hierarchial widget system

# plans, roadmap

- make it work
- make it right
- make it fast, small, stable, bugfree, pretty, etc..

